{"tid":869721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴︰我不認識進攻足球","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T10:03:36.000Z","uid":147522,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f28a84b29929a42c074f953b0b5b2f95c9e594","tid":869721,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"雖然紅魔上場連入3球反勝紐卡素打出精彩一戰，但摩帥始終認為防守才是最重要元素，他說︰「我不懂得進攻足球的哲學，因為你必須先取得皮球才可進攻，當對手控球在腳時你先要防守。」<br />\n<br />\n「我要求我的球隊當對手控球時，盡快把皮球搶回來，而當對手落後時，球隊需要保護防線，又或等候對手犯錯去爭取入球，這些都是與防守有關。」<br />\n<br />\n「當你取得皮球後，你便可進攻，這是依據你所擁有的球員的能力去做。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=615rysS2UWjGrm1Hpz%2F2dsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=aec87c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"914ee047ebfd1ca0a382aeba0f63de2670ecca53","tid":869721,"uid":147097,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T23:47:35.000Z","msg":"廢柴"},{"pid":"4f07183b155d4c06d83ce68c620542777b0e7f4a","tid":869721,"uid":195009,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T23:56:19.000Z","msg":"每當我領先一球 總是把防線壓後 直至被對手扳平和反勝<br />\n<br />\n利申：我曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d12d4527907200f94bc1b7efccbf2d78cc4377c","tid":869721,"uid":1790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"我要求我的球隊當對手控球時，盡快把皮球搶回來<br />\n琴日落後個陣唔覺有做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n追和先有返逼搶"},{"pid":"a2aeb78f21b5eaef260b6aa4744cebf5461f9478","tid":869721,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"摩佬型能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98536228a174fd76071472a47f45d34727ec1e9","tid":869721,"uid":25750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母用返馬仔做進攻核心啦"},{"pid":"311dea6f7927d435ec59017608ef538ba4e8e43f","tid":869